# Copy to .env and fill in real values. Never commit the real .env file.
# OPENAI_API_KEY is consumed by services/llm/client_factory.py as of Stage 5
# (only required when config/setup.json's decision_policy is "llm").
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET_PATH is consumed by services/reporting/gmail_client.py
# as of Stage 8 (only required when using cli/run_series.py's send_report).
# Point it at an OAuth "installed app" client JSON with Gmail access; the
# token is cached in the same folder. The report recipient/repo/group name
# are config-driven (config/setup.json), not environment variables.

OPENAI_API_KEY=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET_PATH=
